These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, american
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, rugby
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, bike
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person driving the van##1
2. the american is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | american    | argentine |
| Sport         | rugby | basketball    |
| Transport     | van     | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, water
There are 2 different nationalities: french, american
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, tram
1. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the french is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | water  | coffee   |
| Nationality   | american | french  |
| Transport     | tram   | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, singing
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, thriller
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, sailing
1. the person who's hobby is singing is in an even position##4
2. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | dancing   | singing  |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | spy  |
| Sport         | basketball   | sailing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
