The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, bike
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the person eating blueberry is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Food          | blueberry | pear |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts   | time-travel   |
| Transport     | bike       | skateboard      |

