The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, camping
2 different pets are kept: mouse, dog
1. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |
| Food    | artichoke | pineapple  |
| Hobby   | camping | photography |
| Pet     | mouse  | dog     |

