.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, board-games
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, argentine
2 different pets are kept: mouse, rat
1. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the nigerian is on the left of the argentine##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | board-games | filmmaking |
| Nationality   | nigerian     | argentine     |
| Pet           | rat          | mouse     |

 #################################

 
