.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-20::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, crime
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: salsa, pop
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, jet-ski
1. the person watching zombie movies is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of pop is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | crime |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | pop  |
| Transport     | jet-ski | train    |

 